metadata.name: Greatest Art Critic Ever
metadata.description:
Profits from the sale of this token will go directly to Free Arts NYC.

Free Arts NYC empowers youth from underserved communities through art and mentoring programs to develop their creativity, confidence, and skills to succeed.

Since its inception in 1997, Free Arts NYC has strived to level the playing field and create equity in the creative space by providing high-quality arts and mentorship programs to the next generation. Free Arts NYC partners with over 40 public and charter schools, community centers, and transitional housing facilities to provide free arts programming to the youth of New York City.
